title: WHAT IF: The Least Asked Question of the Most Successful People, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO265
itunes:title: WHAT IF: The Least Asked Question of the Most Successful People, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO265
description: "What if?" is a question I hear people asking all the time...people who are in the middle of their entrepreneurial journey...or people who are in the midst of trying to accomplish a big goal. The reality is, people who constantly ask themselves that question are mentally abusing themselves. They are subjecting themselves to doubt & uncertainty. Successful people, entrepreneurs or otherwise, are different. They ask entirely different questions and operate under a whole different set of expectations.
